{
     "_id" :  "1-3",
     "chapter" : "CHAPTER 1: MANUAL SNOW AND WEATHER OBSERVATIONS",
     "header" : "1.3 STANDARD MORNING SNOW AND WEATHER OBSERVATION",
     "icon" : "",
"contentHTML" : "<!-- START SWAG content -->
      <main>
        <div class=\"container-lg\">
          <!-- START 1st section -->
          <p>Operations that include an avalanche forecasting program typically
            observe and record a set of weather and snow parameters daily.
            These observations should be made at about the same time each
            day and between 4 am and 10 am local standard time. An example record sheet appears in <a href=\"#figure1-2Accordion\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#figure1-2collapse\">Figure 1.2<\/a>.<\/p>
            <!-- START figure 1-2 accordion -->
              <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"figure1-2Accordion\">
                <div class=\"accordion-item\">
                <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"figure1-2heading\">
                <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed text-info bg-light\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#figure1-2collapse\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"figure1-2collapse\">
                Figure 1.2 Standard observation
                <\/button>
                <\/h2>
                <div id=\"figure1-2collapse\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"figure1-2heading\" data-bs-parent=\"#figure1-2Accordion\">
                <!-- START image -->
                  <img src=\"images\/figures\/1-2.png\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"An example standard observation record sheet.\">
                  <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                   <p>An example standard observation record sheet.<\/p>
                  <\/div>
                <!-- END image -->
                <\/div>
                <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <!-- END figure 1-2 accordion -->
           <p> Many operations
            will need to observe these parameters more than once per day. Listed below is a set of suggested fields to observe and record, and a brief explanation of each. Detailed information on each of
            these parameters is available in the sections that follow. <strong>Sections
            that are marked with a <img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\"> contain information on the parameters listed below.<\/strong><\/p>
            <!-- START steps accordion -->
            <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"stepsAccordion\">
              
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step1Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapseOne\">
                 Observation Location <img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step1Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step1Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the location of the
                  observation site or nearest prominent topographic landmark
                  (mountain, pass, drainage, avalanche path, etc.),
                  political landmark (town, road mile, etc.), or geographic
                  coordinates (latitude\/longitude or UTM). If the measurements
                  are made at an established study site, record the site
                  name or number.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step2Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapseTwo\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapseTwo\">
                Elevation (ASL)<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapseTwo\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step2Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step2Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the elevation of the observation
                  site in feet (meters) above sea level.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step3Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse3\">
                Date<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse3\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step3Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step3Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the date on which the observation is being
                  made (YYYYMMDD).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step4Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse4\">
                Time<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse4\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step4Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step4Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the standard local time on the 24-hour
                  clock (0000â€“2359) at which the observation began.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step5Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse5\">
                Observer<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse5\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step5Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step5Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the name or names of the personnel
                  that made the observation.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step6Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse6\">
                Sky Conditions<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse6\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step6Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step6Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the sky conditions as Clear, Few,
                  Scattered, Broken, Overcast, or Obscured (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.12<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step7Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse7\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse7\">
                Current Precipitation<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse7\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step7Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step7Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the precipitation type
                  and rate using the scale and data codes in <a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.13<\/a>.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step8Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse8\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse8\">
                Air Temperature<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse8\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step8Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step8Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the 24-hour maximum, minimum,
                  and current air temperature to the nearest 0.5 &deg;C
                  (or whole &deg;F) (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.14<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step9Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse9\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse9\">
                Snow Temperature 20 cm (or 8 in)<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse9\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step9Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#stepsCollapse9\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the snow temperature 20 cm (or 8 in) below the snow surface
                  (<a href=\"\">Section 1.17<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step10Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse10\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse10\">
                Surface Penetration<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse10\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step10Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step10Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the surface penetration to
                  the nearest whole centimeter (or 0.5 inch) as described in
                  <a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.18<\/a>.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step11Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse11\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse11\">
                Total Snow Depth<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse11\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step11Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step11Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the total depth of snow on
                  the ground to the nearest whole centimeter (or 0.5 inch)
                  (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.20<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step12Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse12\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse12\">
                24-hour New Snow Depth<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse12\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step12Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step12Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the depth of the
                  snow that accumulated during the previous 24 hours to
                  the nearest whole centimeter (or 0.5 inch) (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.21<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step13Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse13\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse13\">
                24-hour New Snow Water Equivalent<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse13\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step13Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step13Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the
                  water equivalent of the snow that accumulated during the
                  previous 24-hours to the nearest 0.1 mm (or 0.01 inch)
                  (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.22<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step14Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse14\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse14\">
                24-hour Liquid Precipitation<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse14\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step14Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step14Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Record the depth of the
                  liquid precipitation that accumulated during the previous 24
                  hours to the nearest 0.1 mm (or 0.01 inch) (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.24<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step15Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse15\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse15\">
                Wind Direction<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse15\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step15Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step15Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Observe the wind for at least two minutes
                  and record the average wind direction or use an automated
                  measurement. Record wind direction relative to true north
                  as N, NE, E, SE, S, SW, W, or NW. If an automated measurement
                  is used, record to the nearest 10 degrees (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.26<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step16Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse16\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse16\">
                Wind Speed<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse16\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step16Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#stepsCollapse16\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Observe the wind for at least two minutes
                  and record the average wind speed using the indicators in
                  <a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.26<\/a>, or use an automated measurement.<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <div class=\"accordion-item\">
              <h2 class=\"accordion-header\" id=\"step17Accordion\">
              <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed btn-secondary\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#stepsCollapse17\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"stepsCollapse17\">
                Maximum Wind Gust<img src=\"images\/icons\/snow.svg\" alt=\"Icon: Standard Observation\" class=\"icon-sm\">
              <\/button>
              <\/h2>
              <div id=\"stepsCollapse17\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" aria-labelledby=\"step17Accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#step17Accordion\">
              <div class=\"accordion-body\">
                <p>Observe the wind for at least
                  two minutes and record the speed of the strongest wind
                  gust, or use an automated measurement. For an automated
                  measurement record the time that the wind gust
                  occurred (<a href=\"#placeholder\">Section 1.26<\/a>).<\/p>
              <\/div>
              <\/div>
            <\/div>
            
            <\/div>
            <!-- END steps accordion -->
          <!-- END 1st section -->
        <\/div>
      <\/main>"
}
    
